creator: Luxottica Group S.p.a.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome To Luxottica is an application that significantly reduces the waiting time at the reception of Luxottica’s Headquarters.

You can add your contacts, confirm your meetings and check the latest news and updates on the Group’s website and social media accounts directly from your smartphone.
